          Research Fellow, U.S.-Asia Law Institute · NYU School of Law<br>
          Affiliate Research Fellow, AI &amp; the Future of Work · Emory Law<br>
          Member of the New York and Texas Bars
        </p>
        <p class="author-pubs">
          Published in <em>NYU Law Review</em>, <em>UCLA Law Review</em>,
          <em>Minnesota Law Review</em>, <em>Georgetown Law Journal</em>,
          and <em>Vanderbilt Journal of Transnational Law</em>.
        </p>
        <div class="author-links">
          <a href="https://kirinchang.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="author-link">kirinchang.com</a>
          <span class="author-link-sep">·</span>
          <a href="https://github.com/kirinccchang" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="author-link">GitHub</a>
          <span class="author-link-sep">·</span>
          <a href="https://kirin.law" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="author-link">kirin.law</a>
          <span class="author-link-sep">·</span>
          <a href="https://twitter.com/chengchi_chang" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="author-link">@chengchi_chang</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     MODULE 7: FOOTER
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<footer class="footer">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footer-grid">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <div class="footer-logo">
          <span aria-hidden="true">⚖</span> lawreview.tools
        </div>
        <p class="footer-tagline">
          Free, private Bluebook tools<br>for law review editors<br>and legal scholars.
